    <p>Mr Daniel Edid­iong dresses up as Santa Claus for broad­caster In­de­pen­dent Tele­vi­sion in Abuja, cap­i­tal of Nige­ria. “I nor­mally use gloves as Fa­ther Christ­mas, but this year, due to Covid-19, I am us­ing rub­ber gloves, and each time I hand over gifts to chil­dren, I will sani­tise my hands,” said the 36-year-old.</p>

